A mobile app that tracks user activities and offers real-time feedback on eco-friendly choices, helping users become more "Pro Planet." The app integrates with other apps like food delivery and online shopping, nudging users toward sustainable options with pop-ups and fun facts. For example, it might remind users to deselect disposable cutlery while ordering food. The goal is to guide users towards more sustainable behaviors in a fun and engaging way.


